	<div class="network">
            <h4>
                Using the LTE cellular network from AT&amp;T, Sprint, or Verizon
            </h4>
            <p>
                iPad mini with cellular capability lets you connect to fast data networks worldwide — up to LTE.<sup>1</sup>
                So you can connect to the Internet even when Wi-Fi isn’t available.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="no-commitment-data-plans">
            <h4>No–commitment data plans from AT&amp;T, Sprint, or Verizon</h4>
            <p>
                In the U.S., you can choose from data plans with no long-term contract.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="sign-up">
            <h4>Easy signup</h4>
            <p>
                You can sign up for data service right on your iPad mini. And you can monitor your data usage and change your plan at any time, including adding data or canceling service if you know you won’t need it.
            </p>
        </div>
 


			


		
	

