               <img class="ir" src="http://store.storeimages.cdn-apple.com/3226/as-images.apple.com/is/image/AppleInc/2012-ios-step1-applecare-box?wid=70&amp;hei=77&amp;fmt=png-alpha&amp;qlt=95" alt="" width="70" height="77" data-scale-params-2="wid=140&amp;hei=154&amp;fmt=png-alpha&amp;qlt=95" />
